  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exhilarating roguelike action with monsters and swords at your command</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A world where a huge castle suddenly appears.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The protagonist, Rustil, who has no memory of his past, is drawn to the labyrinthine castle.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[<strong>■</strong>Rogue-like action]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your favorite ability from the souls of the heroes lying in the labyrinthine castle and acquire it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a variety of combat styles with one-handed swords, magic staves, gunblades, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162820/extras/332a7c0a5138e5b3e3db7a32c09fc89c.poster.avif?t=1774347676\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162820/extras/332a7c0a5138e5b3e3db7a32c09fc89c.webm?t=1774347676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162820/extras/332a7c0a5138e5b3e3db7a32c09fc89c.mp4?t=1774347676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[■ Treasure Hunt]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mysterious labyrinthine castle that changes every time you enter! <br>Explore its ever-shifting corridors to collect powerful equipment and recruit monsters to join your team!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choose Your Play Style:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Safe Mode</u></strong> <br>A casual exploration mode perfect for relaxed adventuring. <br>Even if your exploration ends in failure, you’ll keep all the items you found.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Challenge Mode</u></strong> <br>A high-stakes mode for those seeking thrill and reward. <br>If you're defeated and fail to return, you'll lose all the items you were carrying. <br>However, the risks come with greater rewards—rare equipment drops more frequently, and it's easier to capture high-stat monsters. <br><i>Note: Even if you lose equipment, you may be able to buy it back from the merchant at home.</i> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162820/extras/63aa74029c90981007fe7add1b70a18c.avif?t=1774347676\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[<strong>■</strong>Monster training and battles]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All monsters in the game can be captured.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can not only improve their abilities, but also decide their personalities in detail!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162820/extras/97e5e70dbf2cb85405e90247a2172cbb.avif?t=1774347676\" width=600 height=338 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162820/extras/5fdd0cb126b23c480350551c5b5dbe1e.poster.avif?t=1774347676\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162820/extras/5fdd0cb126b23c480350551c5b5dbe1e.webm?t=1774347676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162820/extras/5fdd0cb126b23c480350551c5b5dbe1e.mp4?t=1774347676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[<strong>■</strong>Speedy and exhilarating battles]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can enjoy a variety of actions such as one-handed sword, magic staff, and bayonet!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect rare items and capture the labyrinth castle! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162820/extras/8737b6659df4af944e2cad8b1c5f2745.poster.avif?t=1774347676\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162820/extras/8737b6659df4af944e2cad8b1c5f2745.webm?t=1774347676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162820/extras/8737b6659df4af944e2cad8b1c5f2745.mp4?t=1774347676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exhilarating roguelike action with monsters and swords at your command</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A world where a huge castle suddenly appears.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The protagonist, Rustil, who has no memory of his past, is drawn to the labyrinthine castle.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[<strong>■</strong>Rogue-like action]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your favorite ability from the souls of the heroes lying in the labyrinthine castle and acquire it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a variety of combat styles with one-handed swords, magic staves, gunblades, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162820/extras/332a7c0a5138e5b3e3db7a32c09fc89c.poster.avif?t=1774347676\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162820/extras/332a7c0a5138e5b3e3db7a32c09fc89c.webm?t=1774347676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162820/extras/332a7c0a5138e5b3e3db7a32c09fc89c.mp4?t=1774347676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[■ Treasure Hunt]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mysterious labyrinthine castle that changes every time you enter! <br>Explore its ever-shifting corridors to collect powerful equipment and recruit monsters to join your team!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choose Your Play Style:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Safe Mode</u></strong> <br>A casual exploration mode perfect for relaxed adventuring. <br>Even if your exploration ends in failure, you’ll keep all the items you found.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Challenge Mode</u></strong> <br>A high-stakes mode for those seeking thrill and reward. <br>If you're defeated and fail to return, you'll lose all the items you were carrying. <br>However, the risks come with greater rewards—rare equipment drops more frequently, and it's easier to capture high-stat monsters. <br><i>Note: Even if you lose equipment, you may be able to buy it back from the merchant at home.</i> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162820/extras/63aa74029c90981007fe7add1b70a18c.avif?t=1774347676\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[<strong>■</strong>Monster training and battles]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All monsters in the game can be captured.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can not only improve their abilities, but also decide their personalities in detail!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162820/extras/97e5e70dbf2cb85405e90247a2172cbb.avif?t=1774347676\" width=600 height=338 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162820/extras/5fdd0cb126b23c480350551c5b5dbe1e.poster.avif?t=1774347676\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162820/extras/5fdd0cb126b23c480350551c5b5dbe1e.webm?t=1774347676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162820/extras/5fdd0cb126b23c480350551c5b5dbe1e.mp4?t=1774347676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[<strong>■</strong>Speedy and exhilarating battles]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can enjoy a variety of actions such as one-handed sword, magic staff, and bayonet!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect rare items and capture the labyrinth castle! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162820/extras/8737b6659df4af944e2cad8b1c5f2745.poster.avif?t=1774347676\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162820/extras/8737b6659df4af944e2cad8b1c5f2745.webm?t=1774347676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162820/extras/8737b6659df4af944e2cad8b1c5f2745.mp4?t=1774347676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
